  "texts": [
    "In the following, we describe the test cre- ation, administration and scoring procedure with ILAP.",
    "Test creators start by creating a test collection.",
    "This automatically generates a unique and random 4-character access code that the test creator can give to the participants to take the test.",
    "In the next step, tests can be added to the test collection.",
    "The choice for letting the user add different tests into the test collection was made with the future integration of new test types in mind."
  ],
